Munchkin White Hot Safety SunBlock Shade Price: Rs.999

A small baby’s day comprises of sleeping
column15: sleeping consuming most of the hours of his or her day. The Munchkin White Hot Safety Sunblock Shade proves to be helpful to block the sunlight from the baby\u2019s face
column16:
ensuring a calm and peaceful sleep for him or her.

This Sunblock Shade from Munchkin can be conveniently applied to your windows and will help protect the babies from the harmful ultra-violet rays of the sun. This Sunblock Shade from Munchkin is easy to open since it is equipped with a 2-Step Release Button and can be adjusted according to the size of your window. The Suction Cup Pull Handle of this Munchkin White Hot Safety Sunblock Shade makes it accessible and easy-to-use. This Sunblock from Munchkin can be used for both boys can girls.
